Gluten Free Weet-Bix is made from red sorghum grains - not wheat grains.

Sorghum is an ancient grain which is naturally gluten free.

Gluten Free Weet-Bix are made the same way as regular Weet-Bix, except in a separate factory, dedicated to producing gluten free products.

Products.RichDescription:
Grinders Double Espresso Coffee Capsules are strong & intense with chocolatey, nutty & full bodied flavours.


Grinders capsules are for coffee lovers who appreciate the rich, indulgent flavour of cafe coffee, in the convenience of a capsule.

Double Espresso - the truth is in the grind.

Aroma - Nutty
Body - Full
Flavour - Nutty & Chocolate
After-taste - Dark Chocolate

A blend of Arabica & Robusta beans, producing a full bodied coffee, strong & intense. Well defined dark chocolate & nutty flavours, with a long lingering finish.

Perfect for a full bodied espresso, long black, cappuccino, latte or flat white.

Crafted By Master Roasters:

Grinders Master Roasters are the crafters of perfectly balanced roasting.

Their passion and expertise create the deliciously rich, luscious, Grinders coffee flavours you enjoy, cup after cup.

Est. 1962. Lygon St.

Our story started in Lygon St Melbourne, 1962. It was from this humble beginning that Grinders Coffee was born.
